# Google OAuth Client ID — needed for "Download Teacher Guides" export.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
#   2. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID  (Application type: Web application)
#   3. Add your app domain to "Authorized JavaScript origins"
#      e.g. http://localhost:3001  and  https://your-production-domain.com
#   4. Enable the Google Drive API for the project
#   5. Copy the Client ID below and add a real .env file (never commit it)
#
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-oauth-client-id-here
